---
title: Prawn Korma Curry & Onion Chutney with Baby Broccoli & Garlic Rice
description: There's nothing like a mildly-spiced prawn korma curry topped with onion chutney for a warming weeknight meal. Make sure to use the fluffy rice to soak up all that delicious curry sauce!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
